  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/government/news/west-coast-main-line-franchise-competition-cancelled"&gt;West Coast Main Line franchise competition cancelled press notice, 3 October 2012&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/government/speeches/statement-on-west-coast-main-line-and-franchising"&gt;West Coast Main Line and franchising oral statement by the Secretary of State for Transport, 29 October 2012&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
